(3947, 'en', 'default', '0754b49868a7a0ac641085882e136d75', 'You can choose whether or not your site will be crawled by robots, ping services, and spiders. If you want those services to ignore your site, click the checkbox next to &#8220;Discourage search engines from indexing this site&#8221; and click the Save Changes button at the bottom of the screen. Note that your privacy is not complete; your site is still visible on the web.', NULL, NULL, '', 'LINE', NULL, 0, '', '1051f547d613d166e58ee2267ea6046e', '', NULL),
